    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-txt-p dark:text-darkmode-txt-p mb-4">
      光影世界
    </h1>
    <p class="text-lg text-txt-s dark:text-darkmode-txt-s max-w-2xl mx-auto">
